      "raw_text": "CHICAGO. March 30.-W. d.\nHaywood took occasion to criticize\nRoosevelt, Gov. Gooding and other\npublic officials in speech deliver\ned here last night\n\n\nincidentally, Haywood launched\nboom for his candidacy as presi-\ndent of the United States on the So\ncialist ticket Resolutions were\npassed calling for the withdrawal\nof troops at the Treadwell mines\n\n\nSpeaking of the bomb throwing\nin New York Haywood said:\n\n\nwhen some poor, deluded NOR\ntai is trying to take by force what\nby justice belongs to him. we call\n1t outrage, But out in Wyoming\n20 men were killed in a mine ex-\nplosion. That was murder by the\nmine owners\""
    }
